[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Unlocks the built-in dev console with no restrictions, plus a handful of helper commands you'll actually use.[/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][b]Console unlocked[/b] — the developer console commands work without the gating the vanilla game applies.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Helper commands[/b] — adds [code]/finditemid[/code], [code]/printallnpcs[/code], [code]/printallscenes[/code] and a few more to make finding things easier.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]/man &lt;command&gt;[/b] — type [code]/man[/code] followed by a command name to view its full manual right inside the console.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Localised manuals[/b] — command descriptions follow the game's current language setting where translations exist.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Discoverability[/b] — open the chat window and type [code]/[/code] to see every available command listed.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Notes[/b][/size]

[size=3]DLC items are intentionally excluded — they cannot be spawned or added through this mod. That's a deliberate choice to avoid misuse, not an oversight.[/size]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/37]Easy Living[/url] — pairs well: quick-save before you experiment, auto-load to retry quickly.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/207]Museum Sell Price Redux[/url] — once you can [code]/finditemid[/code] anything, museum items become worth chasing.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/426]Seedify[/url] — plant whatever, whenever; combine with [code]/finditemid[/code] for fast crop-testing.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31]Keep Alive[/url] — required by this mod; keeps everything loaded between play sessions.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you installed the required [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/url] and this mod is configurable, press F1 in-game to open the config interface.[/size]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30][size=3]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/size][/url]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31][size=3]Keep Alive[/size][/url]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Compatibility[/b][/size]

[size=3]Built and tested against the latest Windows Steam build of Sun Haven. Other storefronts and platforms aren't extensively tested — should generally work, but YMMV.[/size]

[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[size=3]Installation using Vortex is the recommended installation method. If you wish to install manually, extract the contents of the mod archive into:

[code]...&#92;steamapps&#92;common&#92;Sun Haven&#92;BepInEx[/code][/size]

